OL,3,CConsultants and specialist doctors to
OL,4,Cwalkout in 48-hour strike over pay
OL,6,FThousands of consultants and
OL,7,Fspecialist doctors in Wales have voted
OL,8,Fto strike over pay next month.
OL,10,FThe (BMA) announced their members had
OL,11,Foverwhelmingly voted for 48-hour on
OL,12,FTuesday 16 April.
OL,14,FThe union argues doctor's pay has been
OL,15,Fcut by almost a third in real terms
OL,16,Fsince 2008/09 and want to see
OL,17,Fcompetitive rates of pay and better
OL,18,Fstaffed wards.
