OL,3,CConsultants and specialist doctors to
OL,4,Cwalkout in 48-hour strike over pay
OL,6,FThe say they want to pay doctors more,
OL,7,Fbut cannot afford to without more
OL,8,Fsupport from the UK Government.
OL,10,FAccording to the BMA union, more than
OL,11,F80% of consultants in Wales voted in
OL,12,Ffavour of a 48-hour walkout.
OL,14,Ffrom the BMA have already been on
OL,15,Fstrike twice this year over pay and
OL,16,Fconditions.
OL,18,FThe union says it is committed to
OL,19,Fmaintaining enough cover to ensure
OL,20,Fdoctors can provide emergency care.
