OL,3,CConsultants and specialist doctors to
OL,4,Cwalkout in 48-hour strike over pay
OL,6,F"Unless doctors are better valued for
OL,7,Fthe work they do, more and more
OL,8,Fdoctors will leave an NHS already
OL,9,Funder severe pressure in Wales."
OL,11,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"While we recognise the strength of
OL,13,Ffeeling among members, we are
OL,14,Fdisappointed by the ballot outcome by
OL,15,Fthe BMA and its consultant and
OL,16,Fspecialist doctor members.
