OL,3,CConsultants and specialist doctors to
OL,4,Cwalkout in 48-hour strike over pay
OL,6,F"We agree with the principle of pay
OL,7,Frestoration and will continue to press
OL,8,Fthe UK Government to pass on the
OL,9,Ffunding necessary for full and fair
OL,10,Fpay rises for public sector workers.
OL,12,F"Without that additional funding, we
OL,13,Fare not in a position to currently
OL,14,Foffer any more.
OL,16,F"The 5% increase for 2023-24 is at the
OL,17,Flimits of the finances available to us
OL,18,Fand reflects the agreement reached
OL,19,Fwith the other health unions for this
OL,20,Fyear.
